The paper discusses an image retrieval system that combines visual search with text-based retrieval, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The system also utilizes local features and semantics, which are common techniques in computer vision (cs.CV) and deep learning (cs.DL). The use cases described in the paper involve medical images, which suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories.
